{
  "stem": "1929.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other thing is, you know-- and I'm questioning it, because you would-- normally, you see a close relative that you like, that under no price would you leave them, you would stay with them.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is how other people behave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But was something about me that would not-- had no contact, human contact, in the sense that I wanted to stay.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a-- I was-- turned my feelings off completely.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just was in a survival mode.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just-- my only purpose was to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had no feelings for anything or anybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And anyway, then, they were still chasing us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, finally, I think it was like we were-- we just gave up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We said, to hell with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Let's see what's-- they want us out so badly out of Buchenwald, let's see what's on the other side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was like 3,000 of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the gates of Buchenwald opened up, and we went outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is the first time I've been outside of Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- How long were you there for?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would estimate that I was there about five months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were walking-- as it turned out, we were walking to a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know why they couldn't have loaded us there, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyhow, we were-- we were walking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the one incident that stays-- stands out in my mind to this day, very strongly, is that whoever couldn't walk-- because people were in such horrible physical shape, that they just were not physically able to walk, even half a mile, or a mile.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So whoever could not walk would fall into the side of the road, into a ditch.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
